'''Erwithat''' was the run-down capital city of [[Pembric II]]. It contained the [[ThrusterBurn Tapcafe]] and [[Erwithat Spaceport]]. The city was visited by [[Talon Karrde]] and [[Shada D'ukal]]<ref name="Vision of the Future" /> in [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]]<ref name="Date">''[[The Essential Reader's Companion]]'' dates the events of ''[[Vision of the Future]]'' to [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]].</ref> while looking for [[Jorj Car'das]].<ref name="Vision of the Future" />

